channel.title: How do i add tele's to the emote section or the tele book
channel.description: I was wanting to ad some teles to train, bosses, skill, home, minigames but i dont understand how to add tele's to the telebook or emote section. I need to know how to do this. add teleports.

item.title: How do i add tele's to the emote section or the tele book
item.dc:creator: @aces610 aces610
item.description:
@aces610 wrote:

i want want he gave me i need 2 add a tele.[quote=“Mr. Despair, post:6, topic:337689”][quote author=Phaze One link=topic=434091.msg3187717#msg3187717 date=1271931997]

if (command.equalsIgnoreCase("telehere") && playerRights > 0) toX = xxxx; toY = yyyy; }

I put this since you lack the Java knowledge to do something simple like that -.-. This will add your basic command to teleport somewhere. Fill in the xxxx and yyyy with your desired coords.

He doesn’t want a command you idiot. If you read it he wants to add teleports to the emote interface like Allstar does. Aces find an Allstar base and look in Clickingmost.java. You should be able to find out via there by yourself.
[/quote]

No kidding you arrogant fuck, that’s the same thing I said but if you read above he doesn’t have the knowledge to do that L2R.[/quote]
